# Portfolio Screenshot (Optional: Add a screenshot of your portfolio here)


# 📌  Overview
    Welcome to my personal portfolio website! This platform serves as a digital resume, showcasing my skills, projects, and recommendations. It’s designed to provide an interactive and engaging experience for visitors, allowing them to explore my work and leave recommendations.

# 🎨  Features
    Responsive Design: Optimized for both desktop and mobile users.

    Smooth Navigation: Easy-to-navigate sections for a seamless user experience.

    Projects Section: Highlights my past work with detailed descriptions and links.

    Recommendations Form: Visitors can leave recommendations directly on the site.

    Interactive Elements: Enhanced with JavaScript for dynamic content and interactivity.

# 🛠️ Technologies Used
    HTML5: The backbone of the website’s structure.

    CSS3: Used for styling and creating a visually appealing layout.

    JavaScript: Powers interactivity and dynamic content.

    React: Utilized in some of my projects (as mentioned in my skills).

    Node.js: Backend-related work (if applicable).

